{"title":"红色大别山","authors":["张庆明"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":11,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色大别山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张庆明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一山放过一山拦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山硕果稠，稻浪漫梯田；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一水送过一水迎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草碧牛羊肥，渠水拨琴弦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登山巅呵放眼望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山水水涌心间；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枫如旗呵竹似矛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引我默忆创业艰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年红军战此山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老林撑帐幕，绿草铺地毯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴饮清泉水，饥食野菜团，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热血染枫林，风雨色不变！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我掐把野菜放进口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细细嚼呵慢慢咽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我摘片枫叶揣进怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命火炬胸中燃！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大别山呵，红色的山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先辈握紧枪，打出好江山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大别山呵，革命的山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且看新一代，源源来接班。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈士的热血在我们胸中涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先辈的信念在我们心里闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏着先辈的脚印走呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虎可擒，山可搬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一山放过一山拦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮志如长虹，浩浩贯山川；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一水送过一水迎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豪情似流水，滔滔永不断！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}